Recipient - Class in org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model
Recipient object defines rules for recipient computation
Recipient() - Constructor for class org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model.Recipient
 
RecipientEnum - Enum in org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model
Recipient type enumeration BROADCASTCard is sent to everyone DEADENDCard is sent to no one (Mosty for testing purpose) GROUPCard is sent to a whole group TSODepracated Alias for group UNIONCard is sent to the union of underlying recipients INTERSECTCard is sent to the intersection of underlying recipients USERCard is sent to a specified user FAVORITECard is sent to underlying recipient, if favorite specified user is available, it is set as main recipient RANDOMCard is sent to underlying recipient, a main recipient is randomly set WEIGHTEDCard is sent to underlying recipient, a main recipient is randomly set but a specified user is favored
